      "comment": "ADD A ZERO (1) is a Bobbie-Jean Chaffey-trained newcomer by Sh Avatar out of Zeroed In. Drawn favourably and can capitalise. Has a nice profile and expected to measure up at first outing. OKLAHOMA (4) copped a check in the run and finished a well held 23 lengths seventh (23.71) last time in a Maiden at this track over 380m. Must include in calculations. QUICK TO PARTY (6) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when eighth at this track over 380m behind Phantom's Regret (23.22) in a Maiden. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. CHEESY GARLIC (7) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
